mindmap
  root((ImmoPro - Cameroon Real Estate Platform))
    Current State
      TanStack Router + React 19 + Vite
      shadcn/ui base components
      Demo auth (localStorage)
      Sample bilingual data (FR/EN)
      Express + Mongo backend (solid but not wired)
      Cloudflare + Render deployment intent

    Target Goals (from user)
      Full feature completion
      Production polish
      "AstroJS for optimum SEO, GEO" (clarification needed)
      Premium feel for Douala/Yaoundé/Kribi market

    Skill 1: UI/UX Pro Max (Knowledge + Reasoning)
      161 industry reasoning rules (real estate = trust + premium + local)
      Design System Generator (--design-system)
      161 color palettes aligned to product types
      67 UI styles + 57 font pairings
      99 UX rules (accessibility, touch, forms, navigation first)
      Anti-patterns (especially important for African market trust)
      Output: Tailored design system + rules for this project

    Skill 2: MagicUI (Concrete Components)
      Registry via shadcn CLI (@magicui/...)
      High-impact for real estate:
        Bento grids (property features, neighborhoods)
        Marquee (testimonials, partner agencies)
        Animated stats / counters
        Premium CTAs (shiny, shimmer)
        Hero visuals (globe, warp, aurora for location storytelling)
        Good card interactions & micro-animations
      Complements Pro Max perfectly

    Logic Flow (How the three work together)
      1. Use UI/UX Pro Max
         - Run design-system query for "premium real estate Cameroon" or "luxury property service Douala"
         - Extract color system, typography, style priorities, UX rules, anti-patterns
      2. Define Visual Language
         - Trust + warmth (earth + deep blue/green)
         - Strong photography first
         - Clear hierarchy, excellent mobile experience
         - Subtle, intentional motion (not gimmicky)
      3. Select MagicUI Components
         - Map rules → specific components
         - Example: "Soft UI Evolution + premium" → certain bento + card styles + motion
      4. Implement in ImmoPro
         - Upgrade property cards, hero, dashboard, forms
         - Add missing professional features (real search, maps, booking)
      5. Backend Integration
         - Wire frontend to real Express/Mongo API
         - Add proper image handling
      6. Astro Question
         - If full Astro migration: Astro for marketing + islands for interactive parts
         - Or hybrid (Astro marketing site + React app for dashboard)

    Risks & Gaps Identified (so far)
      Auth is demo-only on frontend
      No real image upload flow wired
      No maps (critical for real estate)
      No advanced search/filters in UI
      Backend has no rate limiting / strong validation yet
      Single-agent model (may need multi-user later)
      SEO currently weak (SPA nature) — explains Astro interest

    Refused Scope (Documented)
      Any hidden /secret destructive admin or kill-switch
      Dispersed components for sabotage
      Anything designed to evade LLM/human audits for malicious purposes
      → This has been explicitly refused and will not be worked on.